    <rdf:type rdf:resource="https://scholarlyontology.aueb.gr/resources/so_schema/so_MLE#Sentence"/>
    <so:sentence_text>However, the subsequent chapter which builds on tephrachronological dating (using volcanic ash deposits) to discuss the application of the technique of tephra contouring (which provides an arguably more quantifiable and representative assessment of landscape) then provides further context.</so:sentence_text>
    <so:is_part_of rdf:resource="https://scholarlyontology.aueb.gr/resources/so_instances/so_MLE#Article/3238498"/>
